task.summary: Added lighting, fixed MiniMap, added random Enemies in rooms, etc.
Added lighting, fixed MiniMap, added random Enemies in rooms, etc.
Added xbox controller support, fixed the MiniMap to display the tiles directly next to one-another, removed doors from the edge of the game, etc.
Added combat (to and from Enemy/Player), added Enemy deaths, added Player death, added GameOver Scene (posts highscores to website), added name input scene, added working doors upon empty room.
Threaded the HighScoreUpdater to prevent lag while adding highscore to the database.
Added Boss level highlighting (YELLOW), added automatic TutorialScene for when controller is plugged in.
Fixed some issues with the highscores being updates multiple times (Added concurrency, thanks Peter), added score system (100 + (hearts * 10)).
Adding custom SplashScreen for our game.
Added TimeAlive counter to the player to add to the HighScores and displayed it on the HUD.
Fixed the setOrigin of the Actor
